metadata.name: Emergence - Where Dreams Land
metadata.description: Emergence is a super-rare airdrop rewarded to the core supporters of the 'Destroy and...' community and core partners who will participate in the future co-construction. Emergence is not only your dojo, whilst also your haven. Here, we will continue to help you break through yourselves, pursue your dreams until you transform, and become the place WHERE DREAMS LAND.
